<div class="feed-main">
<div class="source">
来自 <a href="/topic/19556664" data-tip="t$b$19556664" data-token="19556664" data-topicid="2143">科技</a>

</div>
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" target="_blank" href="/question/35554804#answer-20926848">男士基本款飞行器有哪些？</a></h2>
<div class="feed-question-detail-item">

<a href="#" name="expandQuestionDetail" class="toggle-expand btn-toggle-question-detail ellipsis">现在我更进一步，提前提问，为以后知友们开...&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>显示问题详情</span></a>
<div class="question-description zm-editable-content">
现在我更进一步，提前提问，为以后知友们开拓先路。 我看到了一系列男士基本款问题，在这里，希望大家提前能看到我们需要的基本款飞机，或者是飞船或其他设备。 拜谢！
</div>

</div>
<div class="entry-body "
data-aid="20926848"
data-atoken="63780204"
data-collapsed="False"
data-created="1442319382"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="1"
data-score="0"
data-copyable="1"
>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a name="expand" class="zm-item-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-votecount="681">681</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">赞同</span>
<span class="count">681</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">反对</span>
</button>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">

<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$tsinghuazhou" href="/people/tsinghuazhou">端谨TsHZ</a>，<strong title="镇守Харбин市的野生博士……在读" class="zu-question-my-bio">镇守Харбин市的野生博士……在读</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="681">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$feng-lin-xue-yu-ban-bu-qing-cheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/feng-lin-xue-yu-ban-bu-qing-cheng" class="zg-link" title="枫林雪语半步倾城">枫林雪语半步倾城</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-hao-1-1" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-hao-1-1" class="zg-link" title="刘浩">刘浩</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$need4speed" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/need4speed" class="zg-link" title="Need4speed">Need4speed</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="6428574" data-action="/answer/content">

<textarea class="content hidden">
考虑多数男士&lt;b&gt;真心挚爱一位女士&lt;/b&gt;的需求，&lt;br&gt;首推苏霍伊的苏-27KUB/33UB&lt;b&gt;豪华双人舰载机&lt;/b&gt;。&lt;br&gt;理由如下，多图预警。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;432&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;704&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6e1d7f88bc5d6d46f1713536a639dbc3_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;704&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6e1d7f88bc5d6d46f1713536a639dbc3_r.jpg&quot;&gt;（PS:推荐民航客机的那是空中后宫的节奏么）&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;一、发动机凶猛&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;667&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1000&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/5564b55c243fa181a157a0023bb49260_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/5564b55c243fa181a157a0023bb49260_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;220&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;515&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/32e7fe11558747e44a1202a7be41782d_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;515&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/32e7fe11558747e44a1202a7be41782d_r.jpg&quot;&gt;两台发动机推力加起来二十多吨 &lt;br&gt;推背感9个G &lt;br&gt;百公里200个油 &lt;br&gt;排气管子一米多粗 &lt;br&gt;不服来战&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;二、结实耐艹&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;500&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1000&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b9eb81a59b890b4e432db182da71e82d_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b9eb81a59b890b4e432db182da71e82d_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;男儿有志gang大船  活儿不硬怎能行&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;560&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;596&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/6d1ba146d12bc1e9d52f7e1192a9619a_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;596&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/6d1ba146d12bc1e9d52f7e1192a9619a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;哥是要砸航母甲板的，比你们陆地上起飞的不知道高到哪里去了&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;三、声音呼啸&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;642&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;950&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1193354a432dc445524eb636a2fa2f81_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;950&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1193354a432dc445524eb636a2fa2f81_r.jpg&quot;&gt;这是33UB他亲戚34在拉大过载。破个音障震碎小清新的天空，要么弄个音爆震碎情敌全家玻璃，妥妥的。&lt;br&gt;(请忽略扁铲子头，脑补33UB的前脸)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;四、外形拉风&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;526&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;768&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/efbdac64285303ade6f5698ca005a9c7_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;768&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/efbdac64285303ade6f5698ca005a9c7_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;220&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;366&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/7773b9ff75759b598da1aadc0334586c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;366&quot;&gt;这个…见仁见智吧&lt;br&gt;线条柔中带刚&lt;br&gt;颜值高到可以跟EVA并肩拯da救jiang世you界de&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;五、最关键的一点是，这飞机的座舱是&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;并列双人坐&lt;br&gt;并列双人坐&lt;br&gt;并列双人坐&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;300&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;517&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/39e4151257fcc3773f00362102b3ba6c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;517&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/39e4151257fcc3773f00362102b3ba6c_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/i&gt;也就是它座舱&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;和你家汽车前排正副驾驶座一样&lt;br&gt;深情对视乃至肌肤接触毫无压力&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;为什么不推荐其他串列双人座的飞机呢&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;请看异端&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;220&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;339&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/0d628c9676f7553f79bcb9d480c63eeb_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;339&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;只能看看后脑勺  回头相视都没辙&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;拆散一对是一对  不信空中停个车&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;六、可选装附件【游艇】获得远洋技能加成&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;想象一下在美丽的马里亚纳群岛上，有一艘美丽的游hang艇mu……&lt;br&gt;滑跃甲板上的爱机中，左边坐着一位礼貌的绅士，&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;281&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;549&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/91778aa7066f216595ee0729c1f69929_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;549&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/91778aa7066f216595ee0729c1f69929_r.jpg&quot;&gt;向右望着身边儒雅的女士，微微一笑，&lt;br&gt;说：亲爱的我们去看XX岛好不好呀&lt;br&gt;右边的姑娘羞涩一笑，说：讨厌啦，粗暴点儿好不好~么么哒~~&lt;br&gt;于是，左手猛的推上油门！～&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;317&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;585&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/6b2239d16aa56a17d9ea34e218ec5edd_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;585&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/6b2239d16aa56a17d9ea34e218ec5edd_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;想想就高潮。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;141&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;224&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/bfe02c264ac53a7a76eb470577dfcde5_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;224&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;===========分割线================&lt;br&gt;次推：苏霍伊&lt;b&gt;苏-34豪华双人战斗轰炸机&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;553&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;900&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/0905123bad6e59fa9d0ba151b9ff5920_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/0905123bad6e59fa9d0ba151b9ff5920_r.jpg&quot;&gt;和首推基本一样，唯一缺陷&lt;b&gt;上不了游艇&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;外观是见仁见智的  女士喜欢就好&lt;br&gt;=========再推荐==============&lt;br&gt;卡西莫夫&lt;b&gt;卡-52豪华双人直升机&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;感谢评论区意见&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;600&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;900&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/e8b937ed4d5c15d2b3d9e470efa0f8f9_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/e8b937ed4d5c15d2b3d9e470efa0f8f9_r.jpg&quot;&gt;也能上游艇&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;382&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;600&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/848fbbb25663a471c6820716fc8d0f50_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/848fbbb25663a471c6820716fc8d0f50_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;


<span class="answer-date-link-wrap">
<a class="answer-date-link last_updated meta-item" data-tip="s$t$发布于 2015-09-15" target="_blank" href="/question/35554804/answer/63780204">编辑于 昨天 22:19</a>
</span>

</textarea>
<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img data-rawheight="432" data-rawwidth="704" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/6e1d7f88bc5d6d46f1713536a639dbc3_xld.jpg" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/6e1d7f88bc5d6d46f1713536a639dbc3_r.jpg">
考虑多数男士<b>真心挚爱一位女士</b>的需求，首推苏霍伊的苏-27KUB/33UB<b>豪华双人舰载机</b>。理由如下，多图预警。（PS:推荐民航客机的那是空中后宫的节奏么）<b>一、发动机凶猛</b>两台发动机推力加起来二十多吨 推背感9个G 百公里200个油 排气管子一米多粗 不服来战<b>二、结…</b>

