来自 <a href="/topic/19550461" data-tip="t$b$19550461" data-token="19550461" data-topicid="77">iOS</a>

</div>
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" target="_blank" href="/question/35681704#answer-21009845">iOS 9 正式版的使用体验如何？</a></h2>
<div class="feed-question-detail-item">

<a href="#" name="expandQuestionDetail" class="toggle-expand btn-toggle-question-detail ellipsis">iOS 9正式版已经与2015年9月17...&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>显示问题详情</span></a>
<div class="question-description zm-editable-content">
iOS 9正式版已经与2015年9月17日凌晨1点推送!
</div>

</div>
<div class="entry-body "
data-aid="21009845"
data-atoken="63986995"
data-collapsed="False"
data-created="1442457601"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="1"
data-score="0"
data-copyable="1"
>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a name="expand" class="zm-item-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-votecount="110">110</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">赞同</span>
<span class="count">110</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">反对</span>
</button>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">

<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$xiao-shi-di-92" href="/people/xiao-shi-di-92">胜wang</a>，<strong title="文艺小青年～" class="zu-question-my-bio">文艺小青年～</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="110">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ren-jian-ren-ai-44" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ren-jian-ren-ai-44" class="zg-link" title="人见人爱">人见人爱</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$song-shuang-87" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/song-shuang-87" class="zg-link" title="宋爽">宋爽</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lu-xian-jie" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-xian-jie" class="zg-link" title="吕贤杰">吕贤杰</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="6479359" data-action="/answer/content">

<textarea class="content hidden">
1.小圆点可以设置了，可以增加或减少，比如减少到一个键，直接设为单一home键或者多任务键，方便不少&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/96ed7e4dccd123e3c2cb2fe531b3b81f_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/96ed7e4dccd123e3c2cb2fe531b3b81f_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2.多任务菜单换了，感觉更有翻转性&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/c83856c18e6becd49034ad8be5a3fc60_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/c83856c18e6becd49034ad8be5a3fc60_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;3.主界面左拉有常用的app和联系人&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/82b77083d2af9abc9bd6c23a9d1b8de4_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/82b77083d2af9abc9bd6c23a9d1b8de4_r.jpg&quot;&gt; 4.选取一段话后&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;可以對此修改樣式（好像之前就有，不是新功能，我孤陋寡闻了╮（╯◇╰）╭）&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/df3750cf7b91625e4f0ef0df591a9ff6_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/df3750cf7b91625e4f0ef0df591a9ff6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt; 5.siri的界面更帅气有没有～&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/81352a0b7a18340af3a3d97b3ff828f8_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/81352a0b7a18340af3a3d97b3ff828f8_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6.下拉菜单进去其他app的时候左上角有back to xx的字样&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/eb28a3d44d2b985a8a529a7565bdb2ff_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/eb28a3d44d2b985a8a529a7565bdb2ff_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;7.多了省电模式&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/2c15387e3a2a49cc3621d6407b076347_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/2c15387e3a2a49cc3621d6407b076347_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;8.多了几张系统自带壁纸 ^_^ &lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/38cc50fed9d395f2c67cba56d9af257f_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/38cc50fed9d395f2c67cba56d9af257f_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9.健康应用中多了生殖健康……&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/462c2f526c250f37e0dff10b7debddc5_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/462c2f526c250f37e0dff10b7debddc5_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.备忘录的大改版！&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/d82246f44dc2c5c4f6acb38bc941488a_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/d82246f44dc2c5c4f6acb38bc941488a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;11.字体变了，改为苹方，见以上截图～&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;12.加了照片的预览栏（最下方）&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0cde4e242ed3ff165ee4c3aac60fc87a_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0cde4e242ed3ff165ee4c3aac60fc87a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;分割线——————————————————&lt;br&gt;13.在safari上不需要打开应用，就可以加入备忘录，照片和地图上也有！&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/d8974fc3246b1c28e7f67be38a488502_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/d8974fc3246b1c28e7f67be38a488502_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;14.密码可以设置为6位数&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/bdd90abbb77babc0a4d0991b7be79856_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/bdd90abbb77babc0a4d0991b7be79856_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;15.在ipad上，可以多任务处理，比如这样&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;2048&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1536&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50b0f4313c07d0aef87c40c8cd5bff7f_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;2048&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50b0f4313c07d0aef87c40c8cd5bff7f_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;2048&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1536&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3ae06ebc693c34a28aa82c1da61213a7_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;2048&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3ae06ebc693c34a28aa82c1da61213a7_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9.18更新————————————————&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;16.在ipad上，你打开键盘后，用两支手指在键盘上滑动，可以移动光标，然而感觉并没有什么…………&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;2048&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1536&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/45b06508e713cbbe27085378aa80e567_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;2048&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/45b06508e713cbbe27085378aa80e567_r.jpg&quot;&gt;


<span class="answer-date-link-wrap">
<a class="answer-date-link last_updated meta-item" data-tip="s$t$发布于 昨天 10:40" target="_blank" href="/question/35681704/answer/63986995">编辑于 11:03</a>
</span>

</textarea>
<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/96ed7e4dccd123e3c2cb2fe531b3b81f_xld.jpg" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/96ed7e4dccd123e3c2cb2fe531b3b81f_r.jpg">
1.小圆点可以设置了，可以增加或减少，比如减少到一个键，直接设为单一home键或者多任务键，方便不少2.多任务菜单换了，感觉更有翻转性3.主界面左拉有常用的app和联系人 4.选取一段话后<u><i><b>可以對此修改樣式（好像之前就有，不是新功能，我孤陋寡闻了╮（╯◇╰…</b></i></u>

<a href="/question/35681704/answer/63986995" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="feed-meta">
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el answer-actions clearfix">
