<div class="feed-main">
<div class="source">
来自 <a href="/topic/19552497" data-tip="t$b$19552497" data-token="19552497" data-topicid="763">睡眠</a>

</div>
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" target="_blank" href="/question/23271398#answer-20926497">有哪些可以帮助睡眠的日常物品？</a></h2>
<div class="feed-question-detail-item">

<div class="question-description-plain zm-editable-content">

</div>

</div>
<div class="entry-body "
data-aid="20926497"
data-atoken="63779361"
data-collapsed="False"
data-created="1442318909"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="1"
data-score="0"
data-copyable="1"
>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a name="expand" class="zm-item-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-votecount="76">76</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">赞同</span>
<span class="count">76</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label">反对</span>
</button>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">

<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$xiaoshentongzbt" href="/people/xiaoshentongzbt">小神童周伯通</a>，<strong title="一个么么哒的互联网运营人员 喜欢做饭喜欢diy" class="zu-question-my-bio">一个么么哒的互联网运营人员
喜欢做饭喜…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="76">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$geng-geng-79-66" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/geng-geng-79-66" class="zg-link" title="梗梗">梗梗</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$fuuuun" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/fuuuun" class="zg-link" title="FuuuuN">FuuuuN</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zheng-kai-fu-65" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zheng-kai-fu-65" class="zg-link" title="郑凯夫">郑凯夫</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1489833" data-action="/answer/content">

<textarea class="content hidden">
曾经的我，只要一沾床必睡着，根本不知道失眠为何物~&lt;br&gt;直到失恋···整宿整宿睡不着，不知道是抑郁导致睡不着还是失眠导致抑郁，试过各种办法~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/7c0e4f57482d3a4f7d4cfc85d9380f9a_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;200&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;200&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;200&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;这里不推荐吃安眠药，会有依赖性，虽然我那会也打算去买来着···&lt;br&gt;下面写的基本上都是我用过的方法，链接淘宝随便找的，不负责哒，买的假货不要找人家~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/446ffda940afe7426d8f6fe9952942b5_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;480&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;405&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/446ffda940afe7426d8f6fe9952942b5_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.&lt;a href=&quot;https://detail.tmall.hk/hk/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.13.JIpNAm&amp;amp;id=45026183881&amp;amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;amp;abbucket=13&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;花王眼罩&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;40度左右的温度，直接打开挂耳朵上，价位也还可以，还有各种味道的，很适合直接戴上睡觉。不过也有人说温度不够高，没有热毛巾舒服。。。so，你们看着办~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a6f4781bdb3f4d4c192c99b8ff6e0ba7_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;720&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;562&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;720&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a6f4781bdb3f4d4c192c99b8ff6e0ba7_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2.&lt;a href=&quot;https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.20.qulYye&amp;amp;id=41509245527&amp;amp;ns=1&amp;amp;abbucket=13#detail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;MUJI无印良品 线香香薰&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;无意在muji发现了线香，味道很多，很好闻，就先买了一盒樱花。晚上点上一根，周围萦绕着淡淡的自然香味，有种很安心的感觉。&lt;br&gt;还有薰衣草、檀香、绿茶、柚子、玫瑰、橄榄、牡丹、沉香、树叶、都蛮还原的~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/2eeef4c23106082a11ed3eff28876d1b_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;600&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;600&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/2eeef4c23106082a11ed3eff28876d1b_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3.热牛奶&lt;br&gt;“睡不着？喝杯热牛奶吧。”&lt;br&gt;这是很多电视剧里的台词，其实偶尔睡不着的时候泡杯牛奶还真的有用，和洗个热水澡差不多，身体体温升高就容易产生困意~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/4b1e54053be09434a87d5cfd999d2ea8_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1024&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;576&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1024&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/4b1e54053be09434a87d5cfd999d2ea8_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;4.&lt;a href=&quot;https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.12.s08jed&amp;amp;id=13490527711&amp;amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;amp;abbucket=13&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;褪黑素&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;介个我没有吃过，有个失眠比我还严重的朋友买了，说应该是有效果，但是也有可能是安慰剂···&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/94ffdf44e8088836b06833a9e5153b32_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;800&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;800&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/94ffdf44e8088836b06833a9e5153b32_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;5.功能性app&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.soundario.com/product-pc.php&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;云梦&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;：打开有人声引导，也有背景音乐和场景声音（雨声、森林、海洋等等），就是感觉有人哄你睡觉，挺暖的~如果不想听人声，可以单独关了只听海洋啊雨声什么的，我一般是把人声关小点，放大背景声音，再跟着人声进入睡眠模式~虽然很多人说里面男声很好听，可我只能听女声睡得着~这个强推。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/fae7896fbba9e214991431fc0aa159c4_b.png&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;720&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1280&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;720&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/fae7896fbba9e214991431fc0aa159c4_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;··········不正经的分割线··········&lt;br&gt;最后推荐两个方法，我每次用必定睡着，还睡得特别好&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;杨梅酒，我超爱，每次喝一碗~然后香香哒倒头睡~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/7525bd734a5644c80c21e524734df536_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;690&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;458&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;690&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/7525bd734a5644c80c21e524734df536_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;看物理习题，高一文理还没分班的时候，就是靠这本书让我晚上八点半（刚吃完饭没多久）就睡着~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/bc361ae8e07f1cadc545c878239d06f4_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;960&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;539&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;960&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/bc361ae8e07f1cadc545c878239d06f4_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;不缩了不缩了~&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/634197eb7dcab14366f9294cd8e04d09_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;232&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;197&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;232&quot;&gt;如果你感到有用就给我点个赞~没别的~我只是想红~~~~~~


<span class="answer-date-link-wrap">
<a class="answer-date-link last_updated meta-item" data-tip="s$t$发布于 2015-09-15" target="_blank" href="/question/23271398/answer/63779361">编辑于 2015-09-15</a>
</span>

</textarea>
<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7c0e4f57482d3a4f7d4cfc85d9380f9a_xld.jpg" data-rawwidth="200" data-rawheight="200" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7c0e4f57482d3a4f7d4cfc85d9380f9a_r.jpg">
曾经的我，只要一沾床必睡着，根本不知道失眠为何物~直到失恋···整宿整宿睡不着，不知道是抑郁导致睡不着还是失眠导致抑郁，试过各种办法~这里不推荐吃安眠药，会有依赖性，虽然我那会也打算去买来着···下面写的基本上都是我用过的方法，链接淘宝随便…

<a href="/question/23271398/answer/63779361" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
